basic.Peptide Name: ASP-1 (anti-staphylococcal peptide; natural AMPs; lactone; depsipeptide, bacteriocins; Gram-positive bacteria, prokaryotes; XXE; XXJ, UCSB1b)
basic.Target Organism: Activity: Active against S. aureus NCIM 2901, 5021, and 2127 strains (MIC 2-16 ug/ml), including most MRSA strains (MIC 8-64, but can also be 512 ug/ml).
